OL,4,CMasks 'expected' to be worn in shops
OL,5,Cafter 19 July
OL,6, The government has said it "expects and
OL,7, recommends" shoppers to wear face masks
OL,8, from Monday, but they will not be
OL,9, required by law.
OL,11,FSocial distancing will also not be a
OL,12,Frequirement and people working from
OL,13,Fhome can start to return to work.
OL,15,FThe new guidance leaves firms to decide
OL,16,Fwhat their safety policies will be from
OL,17,F19 July when Covid rules are lifted.
OL,19,FBut it was attacked by employers and
OL,20,Funions, with the TUC calling it "a
OL,21,Frecipe for rising infections".
